"<strong>Live Weight:</strong> Can be logged for any animal status - received "
"animals when truck arrives OR slaughtered animals if forgotten.<br>\n"
"                    <strong>Hot Carcass Weight:</strong> Only for "
"slaughtered/carcass ready animals - weigh in batches after processing.<br>\n"
"                    <strong>Cold Carcass Weight:</strong> Only for carcass "
"ready+ animals - after chilling process.<br>\n"
"                    <strong>Final Weight:</strong> Only for disassembled+ "
"animals - after butchering process.<br>\n"
"                    <strong>Auto-Complete:</strong> When all animals are "
"weighed, individual weights are automatically calculated and saved."
